                {
                    "name": "Irlgaunt Religion",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "A small number of irlgaunts actively worship <a aonid=\"15\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Rovagug</a>, whom they believe to be the progenitor of their species. Instead of living solitary lives, these chaotic evil irlgaunts form cabals that inhabit deep fissures, transforming them into grisly temples by decorating them with the corpses of their sacrifices. They also decorate their own bodies by carving prayers into their chitin and painting themselves with crude and disturbing images. Some claim these runes grant them divine powers of protection and the ability to summon Rovagug's otherworldly kin.",
